properties.property: Welcome! Begin your quest to the SANDWICH MAN. Press your LEFT AND RIGHT arrow keys to move! You can interact with objects giving off similar particles with T!
Press SPACE to jump! Cross this body of water to continue! Collect Coins on the way for your sandwich!

You made it! But it looks like a lever needs to be pulled... Press SPACE while in the air for a double jump. Press and hold an arrow key before the double jump for a dive! Use your newfound knowledge to find a way forward.
This is the lever! What is that down there and slightly to the right though? It looks dangerous... like an enemy. Maybe don't touch that.
This is flag is a checkpoint! Press T when ontop of it to set it at your new spawn! You also get an extra life for interacting with a checkpoint for the first time!
